        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-31" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Critérios de Aceitação" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="280" x="210" y="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;Alta&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O utilizador encontra-se devidamente autenticado no sistema.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O perfil do utilizador está associado a um registo financeiro/conta corrente válida gerida pela tesouraria&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;do clube.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="170" width="1260" x="491" y="-150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema recupera a informação financeira da base de dados e apresenta uma listagem detalhada de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;todos os movimentos associados àquele atleta.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. A visualização é estritamente pessoal e de leitura (&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;55&quot;&gt;read-only&lt;/i&gt;), não permitindo a alteração dos estados de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;pagamento por parte deste ator.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="1260" x="490" y="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. A interface deve permitir filtrar os pagamentos por época desportiva, mês ou por tipo de cobrança (ex:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;quotas, seguros, equipamentos).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O sistema deve exibir de forma inequívoca e com destaque visual (ex: a vermelho ou com um ícone de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;alerta) as quotas ou valores que já ultrapassaram a data limite de pagamento.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O sistema deve garantir a confidencialidade absoluta destes dados, impedindo o acesso por parte de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;outros atletas.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="1260" x="490" y="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
